      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it left the showroom. I've babied this car since day one, so it's flawless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in perfect shape, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 46500.0,
