    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46), maintained to an exacting standard. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled. Power is routed through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to the M-Variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The suspension retains its factory-fresh compliance and damping characteristics. With a flawless exterior and an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
