    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade 2020 Toyota Supra GR Premium in Absolute Zero White. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain, let alone a track. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish; you will find zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. The factory 19-inch forged aluminum wheels are immaculate with no curb rash, wrapped in the original Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires. Inside, the cockpit remains in showroom condition\u2014the black leather sport seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the carbon fiber trim is free of any delamination or scratches. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full service history documented through the local dealership and a clean title in hand. This is an exceptional opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to own a modern icon that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
